2:T702,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Crowdin better than Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Crowdin scores 7.0 overall while Unbabel scores 7.0. Crowdin is best for open-source projects and game developers, while Unbabel excels for customer support teams and global companies."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Crowdin or Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Crowdin starts at Free and Unbabel starts at Custom. Crowdin offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Crowdin to Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Crowdin and Unbabel support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Crowdin vs Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Crowdin holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10. Unbabel has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise Crowdin for great crowdsourcing capabilities and Unbabel for human-quality translation at scale."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Crowdin or Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Crowdin for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Unbabel remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize human-quality translation at scale. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compa